      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but i just dont want to keep running to the doctor every time i want to tweak my vitamins or something. my doctor was super vague and just said 'stay on it'. i feel like if i'm not having any issues, a lower dose is probably just safer for my liver anyway. if i stay around 2mg or 3mg, isn't that still going to keep me protected?",
